==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|gratuitus||free|lang=la}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|gratia||favor|lang=la}}, {{term|gratus||showing favor|lang=la}}

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|UK}} {{IPA|/ɡɹəˈtjuː.ɪt.əs/}}
* {{a|US}} {{IPA|/ɡɹəˈtu.ɪt.əs/}}
* {{audio|en-us-gratuitous.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Adjective===
{{en-adj}}

# Given freely; [[unearned]].
# Not [[call for|called for]] by the circumstances; [[uncalled-for]]; without [[reason]], cause, or proof; adopted or asserted without any good ground; [[unjustified]].
#: '''''gratuitous''' violence''

